snippet.title: SONIC THE HEDGEHOG PC - SAGE 2017 DEMO
snippet.description:
►Download demo at SAGE Expo - https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/sonic-the-hedgehog-sage-2017-demo.53/

►SONIC THE HEDGEHOG is the fan-made PC remake of the original "SONIC THE HEDGEHOG" known as Sonic 2006, using Unity Engine.
